item.description:
@rchurchley 2013-02-06
A disproportionate number of my tweets are exactly 140 characters. I don&rsquo;t know whether that means I&rsquo;m really good at Twitter or really bad.
I don&rsquo;t intentionally set out to do so, but I&rsquo;ve noticed my tweets gravitating towards Twitter&rsquo;s character limit. Sometimes it&rsquo;s the result of a too-long idea being meticulously edited down to size; sometimes it&rsquo;s purely chance. Either way, it&rsquo;s oddly satisfying to post a tweet with exactly 140 characters.
